  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488730/extras/27831db4b2f32bcb6d49b8f33361ffec.poster.avif?t=1771909687\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488730/extras/27831db4b2f32bcb6d49b8f33361ffec.webm?t=1771909687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488730/extras/27831db4b2f32bcb6d49b8f33361ffec.mp4?t=1771909687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Virtual Reality has made playing basketball more interesting, easy, and fun. Take it to the hoop and play the best Virtual Reality basketball game! , complete against the clock to get as many points as you can and try to beat the high score with ultra-realistic graphics and physics.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488730/extras/420f94af7945377ca1205a5b5dfb1f1a.poster.avif?t=1771909687\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488730/extras/420f94af7945377ca1205a5b5dfb1f1a.webm?t=1771909687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488730/extras/420f94af7945377ca1205a5b5dfb1f1a.mp4?t=1771909687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In our VR Basketball Hoops game, you can try shoot hoops with different types of balls not only with the basketballs. <br><br>Install now and shoot some hoops!<br>FEATURES<br>• Stunning Virtual Reality 3d Graphics <br>• Multiple game modes <br>• Play without internet or WiFi<br>• Addictive infinite Game Play<br>• Arcade mode, Time Limit mode, and Dynamic Hoops Mode",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488730/extras/27831db4b2f32bcb6d49b8f33361ffec.poster.avif?t=1771909687\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488730/extras/27831db4b2f32bcb6d49b8f33361ffec.webm?t=1771909687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488730/extras/27831db4b2f32bcb6d49b8f33361ffec.mp4?t=1771909687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Virtual Reality has made playing basketball more interesting, easy, and fun. Take it to the hoop and play the best Virtual Reality basketball game! , complete against the clock to get as many points as you can and try to beat the high score with ultra-realistic graphics and physics.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488730/extras/420f94af7945377ca1205a5b5dfb1f1a.poster.avif?t=1771909687\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488730/extras/420f94af7945377ca1205a5b5dfb1f1a.webm?t=1771909687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1488730/extras/420f94af7945377ca1205a5b5dfb1f1a.mp4?t=1771909687\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In our VR Basketball Hoops game, you can try shoot hoops with different types of balls not only with the basketballs. <br><br>Install now and shoot some hoops!<br>FEATURES<br>• Stunning Virtual Reality 3d Graphics <br>• Multiple game modes <br>• Play without internet or WiFi<br>• Addictive infinite Game Play<br>• Arcade mode, Time Limit mode, and Dynamic Hoops Mode",
